This is a demo of a Django based directory of Federal and State representatives (legislators and 
executives). Data comes from the Sunlight Foundation's python-sunlight package, and Google's 
Civic Information API. Inputs include a zip code, then a map click or an address (number and 
street- added to zip).                                   

The main files are demo/views.py, demo/templates/demo/index.html, and demo/static/demo/style.css.

to run app:
sudo python manage.py runserver 80

Requirements:

Sunlight package (pip install sunlight)
